cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.GT 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category as the paper deals with training deep CNN models for urban semantic understanding. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of simulated virtual environments to train deep CNN models. 
3. cs.GR (Graphics) is another possible category as the paper explores the impact of level-of-realism on the generality of the trained CNN model. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper discusses the use of parametric rendering tool to synthesize data with groundtruth. 
5. cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is another possible category as the paper discusses the use of video games and animated movies to provide training data with high precision groundtruth.
